data.description: Priced to sell! This home 4 bedroom w/ HOME OFFICE or 5 BEDROOM contemporary home sits on a premium lot, featuring a private yard, in the highly desirable Bon-Aire section of Washington Township.  Enter through the CUSTOM DOUBLE DOOR entry w/full lite lead glass insulated doors opening into a tiled foyer with a CUSTOM BUILT wrought iron open staircase. The eat in kitchen boasts 42" CABINETS, soft-close drawers, SLIDE OUT SHELVES, POT DRAWERS,  and a LARGE PANTRY with slide out shelves, recess lighting, GRANITE COUNTER TOPS, Stainless steel KENMORE APPLIANCES!! The breakfast area features a BUMP OUT NOOK  giving you extra space for a big table and offers an open layout into the cozy family room with STONE DECORATED GAS FIREPLACE. The laundry/mud room off the family room leads out to the oversize two car garage, equipped with Clopay INSULATED GARAGE DOORS with separate openers! Formal dining room opens to the spacious family rm with VAULTED CEILINGS and SKY LIGHTS and offers a great area to entertain! The HUGE MASTER BEDROOM upstairs also has a SOARING VAULTED CEILING, DOUBLE WALK IN CLOSETS, and a SITTING AREA/DRESSING AREA. The large marble covered master bathroom features a 2 person GLASS stand up shower, plus a jet-SOAKING TUB and stone vanity, and yes, vaulted ceilings! The other 3 bedrooms all have ceiling fans and BIG CLOSETS. As if thats not enough, the FINISHED BASEMENT gives you added space for entertaining along with a good sized unfinished rooms that provides TONS OF EXTRA STORAGE space. The back yard offers a little for everyone. Relax on the PATIO under the Pergola, or shoot some hoops on the basket ball half court, this yard has the space to spread out and is private! Some EXTRA upgrades include NEW WATER SOFTENER system, New Light Fixtures w LED lights t/out, NEST Thermostat, Solid 6 Panel Doors all w/oil rubbed bronze hardware, High Efficiency HVAC, Sprinkler System! Priced well under market value for the area, needs a little tlc to bring it back to the condition in the photos!
